		"body": "**Solved**:  https://github.com/laurent22/joplin/issues/14391\r\n\r\n**This PR resolves the recurring to-do reminder request by finalizing RRULE-compatible alarm behavior:**\r\n\r\n-> Adds recurrence storage and migration support via notes.alarm_recurrence.\r\n\r\n-> Wires recurrence through alarm scheduling and due-note processing.\r\n\r\n-> Adds desktop recurrence selection in the alarm flow and clears recurrence when alarms are cleared (desktop/mobile).\r\n\r\n-> Fixes recurrence logic to parse both FREQ and INTERVAL, enabling schedules like every 2 weeks/months/years to calculate the next trigger correctly.\r\n\r\nThis closes the gap where recurrence existed but interval-based RRULEs were not respected during next-trigger computation.\r\n",
